name: Motoko Kusanagi | Ghost in the Shell Sac_2045
description:
LoRa trained with the Revanimated model (but it should also work with other models).

The mayor Motoko Kusanagi from Ghost in the Shell SAC 2045 was eager to create images of this character, so I decided to create the LoRa xD, the recommended weight is between 0.5 and 0.7.

Remove the trigger words: black gloves, black jacket, leotard, to make it with different clothes (or without anything).

For an anime style use: (use v1.1)

For 3D style use: (3D:1.4) and (CGI:1.2)

Also available on pixai.art to generate images online: https://pixai.art/model/1616776971809363183

That's all, enjoy it!

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description:
This version is trained with the Hasakku model (Hentai model), which makes it easier to create NFSW images, in addition to giving a more anime style easily (the previous version is perfect for a more 3D style).

the recommended weight is 0.5 to 0.8

In this version it is easier to generate different types of clothing (and without it too)

enjoy it!!
